---
title: Mumbai Beef Meatball & Green Bean Curry with Garlic Rice & Yoghurt
description: Get ready to fall head over heels for this rich, hearty dish that’s a splendid symphony of flavours. The secret is cooking up the curry in
a single pan so the tender meatballs soak up the traditional Indian spices. With a bed of fluffy garlic rice to finish it off, you better be
ready to savour every taste – it’ll be gone before you know it!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6397a903a378dc5340028372-cd9a9946.jpg
